Dumun is reported to go by the name '''Bai''', but evidently this is a distinct (though related) language, or at least a variety called Bai recorded by Maclay was distinct.<ref>[https://www.academia.edu/2843435/Systematic_typological_comparison_as_a_tool_for_investigating_language_history]</ref><ref name="Glottolog2" />
